*Njeno* srce otkucava od strasti. (Her heart is pounding with passion.)
*Njenom* obrazovanju nikada nije prestajala da se divi. (She never ceased to marvel at her education.)
*Njene* oči su bile uprte u horizont. (Her eyes were fixed on the horizon.)
*Njena* reč je bila zakon. (Her word was law.)
*Njegovo* ponašanje je uznemirilo njenu porodicu. (His behaviour disturbed her family.)